flowchart TD
    A[Real-world problem<br/>schedule, diagnosis, molecule] --> B[Turn it into math<br/>a circuit or a cost function]
    B --> C[Quantum computer or simulator<br/>runs the circuit]
    C --> D[Measure the qubits<br/>get a noisy answer]
    D --> E[Classical computer<br/>checks and refines]
    E --> F{Good enough?}
    F -->|No| C
    F -->|Yes| G[Final answer]
    G --> H[AI writes it up<br/>in plain English]

    style A fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1565C0
    style C fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#4527A0
    style E fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32
    style H fill:#FFF8E1,stroke:#F9A825
